    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the \"not as stuck as i think\" part... i dont know. it doesnt feel like i'm just stuck. it feels like the thing that was actually alive, the part that had purpose and felt things... that part is just gone. permanently. it's like there's nothing left in here but the habit of breathing.",
